{"tid":591270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"超噁偏方！她「生吞3青蛙」治風濕　乳房長13公分條蟲","createTime":"2018-03-13T11:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T16:49:51.000Z","uid":22675,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bfa47356541833f2704b551057d1b26616c42179","tid":591270,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"大陸浙江省1名59歲的姚姓婦人長期受風濕症所苦，但她卻誤信偏方，認為只要生吞「3隻活青蛙」就能治病，之後卻開始出現嚴重腹痛，痛苦難耐之下只好就醫。沒想到，醫生檢查後驚見，患者的體內竟遭蟲卵寄生，進而導致腹痛、眼睛疼痛、乳房腫脹等症狀，最後還在胸部腫塊中發現1條長約13公分的條蟲。<br />\n<br />\n據大陸《看看新聞》報導，姚婦長期患有風濕症，但她5年前聽信當地老人所言，認為只要生吃青蛙，就能治好所有身體病痛，且吞了青蛙後還不能對別人說，否則會效果盡失等語，最後偷偷地生吞了3隻青蛙；不料，姚婦的風濕症不但沒有改善，還開始出現腹痛情況，痛得她趕緊到醫院求助。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，姚婦就醫後被確診為寄生蟲感染，事後輾轉前往上海治療，雖然腹部不再疼痛，但接連出現其他症狀，包括眼睛不適和乳房腫脹等；直到醫生近日替病患進行手術，準備切除其胸部腫塊，卻意外在硬塊裡發現1條長約13公分的白色條蟲。<br />\n<br />\n主治醫師表示，該蟲是「曼式裂頭蚴」，屬於條蟲的1種，平常多寄生於貓、狗等動物，在人體上發現的案例甚為少見，研判應是藉由生青蛙進入體內，起先還是蟲卵時，先在腹內引起腸梗塞，之後孵化為幼蟲便開始在體內亂鑽，所以才會造成患者病症不斷。"},{"pid":"6b2c50cc03bec8d765ff2ecd9be5f9bcf349f6bd","tid":591270,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0d2aa40ad75a4d423d73ead29bd901457b1aca","tid":591270,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:16:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/881831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fworld%2F881831&d=IhKlETWeGwy2SRW03p3ARgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=2ca1c7ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/881831</a>"},{"pid":"b659ab6a022737e4926dcaabd0ff7e036f4e5ffd","tid":591270,"uid":144883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:23:47.000Z","msg":"身為支那人，食果幾隻生青蛙都出事？"},{"pid":"bb8537ebc89ce89a7bdd185139e9f3f77885eb5c","tid":591270,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:29:09.000Z","msg":"又冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9eee34bd3106b7483fefd7e310bd4570b11d4ce","tid":591270,"uid":80176,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:35:17.000Z","msg":"個老人叫人唔好講<br />\n分明玩鳩個女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25674abeb2ce58336e2c3fe043765ef88575fd83","tid":591270,"uid":174074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:35:47.000Z","msg":"好恐怖 蟲卵"},{"pid":"25d22ceac876f4e03e09cbdb4f7f82adf648213c","tid":591270,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:41:36.000Z","msg":"D記者分唔分到條字同絛字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bd74f3d437a5da976fb996ea09a52b9e3ad9a8","tid":591270,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d79f202bb9fcc9ab9cf20a85caf13c7d18bfcd","tid":591270,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:49:25.000Z","msg":"冇撚腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e35cd354e839515c4fb655d7d5f1b38ebb4246","tid":591270,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:51:50.000Z","msg":"呢種蟲會上腦"},{"pid":"bf7c997d8bbf28ec7044cacfa43175efdacc77f2","tid":591270,"uid":818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T13:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa